title: Arctic Monkeys UK Tour 2006
name: Arctic Monkeys UK Tour 2006
description:
A Map by Lolly

You can find the gigs, go to the shows, then when you get home you can add all the cool pictures you took to the map. Just click on the show you went to and then click &quot;add images.&quot; You have to use image urls, so put the pictures on flickr first. Meet other people who went to the same gig by posting comments!

properties.name: Arctic Monkeys, Sat 8 July 2006
properties.description: Posted by Lolly OxegenOXEGEN 2006 THE ARTIST\'S AND AUDIENCE\'S ULTIMATE MUSIC FESTIVAL! Check out the acts in the line up section! Never before has there been such huge anticipation about the launch of OXEGEN and it gives festival organisers great pleasure to announce the launch of 2006\'s fantastic festival. Voted Ireland\'s number 1 festival by music fans, the artist\'s and audience\'s favourite festival returns boasting a truly spectacular line up for 2006. OXEGEN guarantees yet another completely unique experience for the festival fans at Punchestown on Saturday 8th & Sunday 9th July 2006 subject to licence.
